{"tid":188095,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"後生仔比下意見","createTime":"2017-04-05T12:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T00:29:18.000Z","uid":75299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"22288b7efb1715896aa36bc6b7d7fe410e83f035","tid":188095,"uid":75299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:09:08.000Z","msg":"我今年47，一年前做左大手術，身體一直麻麻，成日有後遺症<br />\n<br />\n同公司講左叫佢培養新人，但係又揾唔到好人選<br />\n<br />\n今日再講退休問題，公司叫我聽日返去頃返半日休半日。<br />\n<br />\n我係老一輩人，唔想欠公司太多，我手術費公司保險比左廿十萬，加二個月病假<br />\n<br />\n我已經幫公司培養左兩個後生仔，但係公司都係唔鐘意<br />\n<br />\n想問下你地後生點睇，有乜意見？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013bc71b9f2e1c8ce6b1943cce3c154498ebae1e","tid":188095,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:10:35.000Z","msg":"。。單簡，換左個老細"},{"pid":"f861b5446833fb5c14ee678dad576ddec40d1360","tid":188095,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:10:45.000Z","msg":"唔係要問你公司有咩意見咩？<br />\n兩個人train 完出嚟都唔要唔係你問題喎"},{"pid":"fe39bc0be01ce923feef544d8854224db7fb0441","tid":188095,"uid":75299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:13:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係要問你公司有咩意見咩？<br />\n兩個人train 完出嚟都唔要唔係你問題喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我好比心機train, 但唔知點解佢地成日唔小心，同埋天份真係麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2646cc151f11504d16a35325c70f99f559fa34b9","tid":188095,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:14:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係要問你公司有咩意見咩？<br />\n兩個人train 完出嚟都唔要唔係你問題喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我好比心機train, 但唔知點解佢地成日唔小心，同埋天份真係麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你份工咩性質 GA?"},{"pid":"61428c0d71feab7005479b4f9e973f3e2313dd44","tid":188095,"uid":75299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:22:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係要問你公司有咩意見咩？<br />\n兩個人train 完出嚟都唔要唔係你問題喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我好比心機train, 但唔知點解佢地成日唔小心，同埋天份真係麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你份工咩性質 GA?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  IT狗，不過係 management 同埋金融業，我有超過廿十年經驗"},{"pid":"823249f8443ef6531cae43b7bf2a19874f57ebb3","tid":188095,"uid":66788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:29:49.000Z","msg":"你抖下啦 <br />\n身體先最重要<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你盡力做左你本份既野 係個2位後生未識點生性啲 <br />\n<br />\n你好努力架啦 <br />\n比多啲時間自己同比屋企人"},{"pid":"72b8e01fc50c1557574c9b4cf8df0a76162822ee","tid":188095,"uid":24924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:35:06.000Z","msg":"有兩個新人你就應該可以退場啦 <br />\n除非兩個𡃁仔真係好唔掂 咁你同公司傾限期 番多半年就半年 傾好左就唔好猶豫"},{"pid":"f3c6ea44665c3057ac3e00f3f175719f1701d766","tid":188095,"uid":75299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:17:38.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打，聽日頃完會回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e3bd3dcc423fd33e4581c6d2032446e183466d","tid":188095,"uid":75299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:19:35.000Z","msg":"講好左了，返多一個月半日，可以走得，如果有需要，會用計件方式做下顧問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要再計劃生活了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ebe68ab17434d1af9e3e83d3672c0a34465760","tid":188095,"uid":32947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T00:29:18.000Z","msg":"睇個人造化呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條友話頭醒尾既話 自動會double check同會留意有經驗個班做野果套方式"}]}